{"tid":134735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太鬆軟咪掂】深圳酒樓賣鋁饅頭 食得多變癡呆","createTime":"2017-02-25T16:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T03:29:39.000Z","uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33ef6938140290d83e405aab514e551132c9de93","tid":134735,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170226&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56353894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170226%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56353894&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=7a94c5a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170226%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56353894&h=0ae3203b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170226&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56353894</a><br />\n深圳一間酒樓為了令饅頭鬆軟，竟然違規在麵粉裏添加大量含鋁的添加劑。該酒店的廚師說：「我們用自己的配方去做的，我們就是加糖啊，加那些材料上去。」<br />\n鹽田食品藥品監督管理局前日突擊抽查時，發現每公斤饅頭裏含鋁成份達339毫克，而根據國家規定，饅頭不得添加含鋁成份。酒樓的涉事廚師已辭職。<br />\n內地專家指，太過鬆軟的饅頭確實有「鋁」超標的風險。人體不需要鋁元素，如長期超量攝入，鋁會沉積在大腦、骨骼等組織當中，累積到一定數量後產生慢性毒副作用，引起神經系統的病變，導致沉積在骨質中的鈣流失，同時抑制骨的生成，可能促進骨質疏鬆症、記憶力衰退，甚至癡呆，還會使皮膚皺紋增多。此外，鋁對造血系統和免疫系統有一定毒性，同時妨礙鈣、鋅等多種元素的吸收。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCQ0z5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCQ0z5q.jpg&h=4d9afcc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca50697e60aac6707179f0ce5681c9ea0df82f74","tid":134735,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170226&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56353894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170226%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56353894&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=7a94c5a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170226%26s%3